message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This item is truly a masterpiece and offers unparalleled value. Given its significance and the benefits it provides, we believe it's worth more than $8,000. Considering its true worth to you, we're offering it at a special introductory price of $10,000. This is an exclusive opportunity to own something truly exceptional. Please let us know if this aligns with your expectations and budget.
